init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The beach is your soul and the grain of sand that's giving a part of itself to its own spirit is you.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: can choose what role you're going to play

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The experience of watching each life on the big screen is very enlightening, and you realize how much more value you have in each life when

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: you compare them to the life that you just watched.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So now that you've been watching your past life, you realize that it's time to go back in.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's time to play the next life.
